artist: Artist: Roberto Sebastian Matta; Publisher: La Biennale de Venezià, 1974
creditline: Acquired through the Minnesota Museum Property Act
description: Issue 2 of 5 of a newspaper published during the 1974 Biennale di Venezia with a poster insert by Roberto Matta; newspaper type in black and orange inks; poster is white with figures and animals drawn in thick black lines; HAY QUE ABRIR LOS BRAZOS COMO SE ABREN LOS OJOS appears in a speech bubble on the lower right side of the poster
medium: Offset lithography and letterpress in black and orange
title: Issue 2 of Libertà al Cile: Liberstad para Chile, La Biennale di Venezià, 1974
